OL,3,C'My hardest decision' - Trent
OL,4,CAlexander-Arnold to leave Liverpool
OL,6,FAlexander-Arnold helped Liverpool win
OL,7,Fthe Premier League this season.
OL,9,FThe success moved the Reds level with
OL,10,Frivals Manchester United on 20 top-
OL,11,Fflight titles.
OL,13,F"I know many of you have wondered why
OL,14,For been frustrated that I haven't
OL,15,Fspoken about this yet, but it was
OL,16,Falways my intention to keep my full
OL,17,Ffocus on the team's best interests,
OL,18,Fwhich was securing No.20," continued
OL,19,FAlexander-Arnold's statement.
