OL,4,CAlexander-Arnold to leave Liverpool
OL,6,F"This club has been my whole life ` my
OL,7,Fwhole world ` for 20 years. From the
OL,8,FAcademy right through until now, the
OL,9,Fsupport and love I have felt from
OL,10,Feveryone inside and outside of the
OL,11,Fclub will stay with me forever.
OL,13,F"I will forever be in debt to you all.
OL,14,FMy love for this club will never die."
